changelog.comment: Initial entry. Reviewer 1 supplemented description of known reaction to include measured increased enzyme activity in presence of Cobalt(II).

reactions.description: Cleaves modified bottromycin precursor peptide between thiazole8 and Met9.
bottromycin A2-precursor peptide after methylation, hetero- and macrocyclization. Higher activity of enzyme measured in presence of Cobalt(II).
